            "title": "Clutter‐adaptation of bat species predicts their use of under‐motorway passageways of contrasting sizes – a natural experiment",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "I. M.",
                    "lastName": "Abbott"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
